A shocking CCTV footage of a UK man being hit by a bus and then walking as if nothing happened, has been doing the rounds on social media.In the video the man is seen walking on the edge of the road, when suddenly a bus that is out of control hits him. &nbsp;Simon Smith was knocked to the ground by the bus but was able to get back on his feet afterwards and suffered bruising.It is said that he walked into a local pub called Purple Turtle after the incident.WE ARE OPEN! The bus didn't hit the Purple Turtle. Just in case you weren't sure!&mdash; Purple Turtle (@PurpleTurtleRdg) June 27, 2017